text: Hi, I'm Sarah from Flashbots, and today I'm here to introduce FRP at the FRP on conference. SRP is administered through this GitHub repo, and in order to submit a proposal, you would copy this template and give us background on your area of interest, the background for the problem, and also the research problem statement, the plan for how you want to tackle it, and the deliverables that you'll produce, and then references to past work in the area. We'll consider the proposal, and our team will get back to you within a couple of weeks with either questions, comments, or a funding decision.
